name: Air Fryer Oreos®
author: Yoly
summary: Craving that carnival food? With just 3 ingredients and an air fryer, you can make fried Oreos® at home!
ingredients: 1 tablespoon confectioners' sugar, or to taste
directions: Mix pancake mix and water until well combined
Line an air fryer basket with parchment paper
Spray parchment paper with nonstick cooking spray
Dip each cookie into the pancake mixture and place in the basket
Make sure they are not touching; cook in batches if necessary
Preheat the air fryer to 400 degrees F (200 degrees C)
Add basket and cook for 4 to 5 minutes; flip and cook until golden brown, 2 to 3 minutes more
